### Search for Books by Title
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/search?title=Pride and Prejudice
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Search Books with Pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/search?title=Java&page=1&size=2
Content-Type: application/json


